graph TD
    Root["/ (ZooKeeper Root)"] --> HA["hadoop-ha"]
    HA --> NS["mycluster (Nameservice node)"]
    NS --> Lock["ActiveStandbyElectorLock (Ephemeral ZNode)"]
    NS --> Breadcrumb["ActiveBreadcrumb (Persistent ZNode)"]

    Note over Lock: Ephemeral Node. Stores hostname and <br/>port of the ACTIVE NameNode.<br/>Session lost = ZNode deleted.
    Note over Breadcrumb: Persistent Node. Stores the last known <br/>Active NameNode identifier.<br/>Prevents split-brain by identifying <br/>prior active node during boot.
